scenes.description: Nanashi Mumei and Inugami Korone continue their 3D interaction. Mumei uses an owl plushie (Hooty) as a ball for Korone to hit with a giant hammer. They take selfies together before Korone departs.
Instrumental transition to a new scene with Mumei and Polka in yukatas.
Nanashi Mumei and Omaru Polka perform the song 'No title' in a traditional Japanese setting.

subtitles.original: Lyrics/Composition: Reol
subtitles.english: Lyrics/Composition: Reol

subtitles.original: ずっとなりたかった僕になれたかな
subtitles.english: Did I become the person I always wanted to be?

subtitles.original: 到底抗えないところまできてみたい
subtitles.english: I want to reach a point where I'm completely unstoppable

subtitles.original: 自分の足で地を蹴飛ばして
subtitles.english: Kicking the ground with my own feet

subtitles.original: もっと先へ駆け抜けていけるはずだから
subtitles.english: Because I should be able to run even further

subtitles.original: On the way...
subtitles.english: On the way...

subtitles.original: ずっと鳴り止まなくて
subtitles.english: It won't stop ringing

subtitles.original: ずっとばち当たりに這い回りたかった
subtitles.english: I wanted to crawl around like a curse

subtitles.original: 慣れた痛み 焦る呼吸とbeat
subtitles.english: Familiar pain, racing breath and beat

subtitles.original: 気づかない振りして待つひとり
subtitles.english: Pretending not to notice, waiting alone

subtitles.original: 相反する内なるエゴ
subtitles.english: Conflicting inner ego

subtitles.original: 誰か間違いだと言い放つまで
subtitles.english: Until someone says it's a mistake

subtitles.original: あんたが大嫌いなアイツはきっと
subtitles.english: That person you hate so much is surely

subtitles.original: 誰かそれだけが正解なんだって
subtitles.english: The only correct answer for someone

subtitles.original: 前線だって逆戦したって 全然納得できない理由も
subtitles.english: Even on the front lines, or even if I fight back, reasons I can't accept at all

subtitles.original: 宣戦もいつだってここだった
subtitles.english: The declaration of war was always here

subtitles.original: 存在を今日最初から待った
subtitles.english: I waited for my existence from the beginning today

subtitles.original: 夕焼空に崩れ壊れていく
subtitles.english: Crumbling and breaking into the sunset sky

subtitles.original: ゆらりゆらり首を絞めるように
subtitles.english: Swaying, swaying, as if strangling my neck

subtitles.original: 日の目の僕が殺されていく
subtitles.english: The "me" in the sunlight is being killed

subtitles.original: 夕焼空に離ればなれや
subtitles.english: Parting ways in the sunset sky

subtitles.original: どなりに君に聞こえるのは
subtitles.english: What you hear next to you

subtitles.original: 僕の知らない声になって
subtitles.english: Is becoming a voice I don't know

subtitles.original: 幼い日の僕ならば 気づいたらそばにいた
subtitles.english: If it was the me of my childhood, I found you by my side before I knew it

subtitles.original: まるで月夜のようだ
subtitles.english: It's like a moonlit night

subtitles.original: 都会 君だけと手を繋いで
subtitles.english: In the city, holding hands with only you

subtitles.original: 楽しいことも涙も
subtitles.english: Fun things and tears too

subtitles.original: 全部君に話して聞かせていた
subtitles.english: I told you and let you hear them all

subtitles.original: 僕を笑う人へ貶す声
subtitles.english: The voices of people belittling me, laughing at me

subtitles.original: 掻き消すように君は歌った
subtitles.english: You sang as if to drown them out

subtitles.original: この声を君が信じて支えてこれたから
subtitles.english: Because you believed in and supported this voice

subtitles.original: 嘘だって言って去って
subtitles.english: Saying it was a lie and leaving

subtitles.original: 詰まらない敗北さえとかい
subtitles.english: In the face of boring defeats or whatever

subtitles.original: 一瞬巡る窓ただ一瞬だけでも
subtitles.english: A window passing for a moment, even for just a moment

subtitles.original: 交わる言葉を繋ぐ色
subtitles.english: Connecting colors that join words

subtitles.original: 次は僕が君に歌うから
subtitles.english: Next, I will sing for you

subtitles.original: 夕焼空に崩れ壊れていく
subtitles.english: Crumbling and breaking into the sunset sky

subtitles.original: ゆらりゆらり首を絞めるように
subtitles.english: Swaying, swaying, as if strangling my neck

subtitles.original: 日の目の僕が殺されていく
subtitles.english: The "me" in the sunlight is being killed

subtitles.original: 夕焼空に...
subtitles.english: In the sunset sky...
